linux-sky1 (6.18.1-sky1.5) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Change core Sky1 Kconfig entries from tristate to bool
    - Core SoC infrastructure (mailbox, reset, pinctrl, clk, pci,
      hwspinlock, PHYs) must be built-in
    - Board-specific drivers (PWM, watchdog, socinfo, Type-C) stay tristate

